options.markdown:
####Built-in Dashboards: This built-in dashboard was created using memory statistics metrics derived from the expvar variable `memstats`. The charts summarize memory allocation metrics of multiple expvar instrumented Go applications.

####Custom Dashboards: Additional dashboards can be created using the default metrics this integration collects and/or any user-defined ones.

options.markdown:
####Built-in Dashboards: This built-in dashboard was created using memory statistics metrics derived from the expvar variable `memstats`. The charts are filtered by application name, host and port to show detailed memory allocation metrics of a single expvar instrumented Go application.

####Custom Dashboards: Additional dashboards can be created using the default metrics this integration collects and/or any user-defined ones.
